  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its overall size, materiality and location in a high risk area of surface water flooding, would significantly increase the impermeable surfacing of the site, resulting in increased potential for surface water flooding and excess water run off, contrary to policy SI12 (Flood risk management) of the London Plan (2021) as well as LP53 (Water and flooding) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its overall size, materiality and loss of vegetation/soft landscaping, would result in an unsympathetic, uncharacteristic and intrusive form of development that would fail to respect the local context and character of the surrounding area and results in a significant loss biodiversity on site without remediation.&amp;nbsp; As such the proposed development is contrary to policies D4 (Delivering good design) and G6 (Biodiversity and access to nature) of the London Plan (2021) as well as LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP47 (Biodiversity and Sites of Importance of Nature Conservation) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
